body:
Please go through the documentation [to convert tf model into tensorflow lite](https://www.tensorflow.org/lite/convert/python_api#exporting_a_tfkeras_file_)  and [additional instructions](https://www.tensorflow.org/lite/convert/python_api#additional_instructions) if you haven't already. 

In addition, can you please try tf-nightly and check if the issue still persists?
